::Battera::

She continued along until she came across what she thought was one of the 
cargo bays. It had the rafters that were way up high.  She smiled at a a 
thought she had.  She flew up to the rafters and hung up-side down and 
closed her eyes.  She liked being up off the ground.  She stayed alert to 
noises so as to know when and if someone was coming.
